m ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Turpis in in leo velit turpis at. Sed vivamus amet elementum lobortis pretium enim elit volutpat dignissim. Diam sit non amet at ipsum. In faucibus amet nulla amet. <\/p>","description_hn_replace":false,"show_more":false,"text_max_lines":3,"text_more":"Voir plus","text_less":"Voir moins","show_more_alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["heading_q86bJM","text_t7Cbdq"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"text_alignment":"left","no_vertical_padding":false,"image_restricted_width":false,"image_adapted_height_with_content":false,"contain_image":false,"layout":"image_first","mobile_layout":"image_first","overlay":true,"overlay_opacity":0.2,"section_color_scheme":"","color_scheme":"scheme-2","padding_top":48,"padding_bottom":48}},"ax_image_with_text_x3wFzW":{"type":"ax-image-with-text","blocks":{"subheading_JWwFUp":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"subheading":"SUB HEADING"}},"heading_LzyUxg":{"type":"heading","settings":{"picto_size":24,"picto_size_mobile":24,"heading":"<p>LOREM IPSUM DOLOR<\/p>","heading_size":"h2"}},"text_mqaabX":{"type":"text","settings":{"picto_size":24,"picto_size_mobile":24,"text":"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Etiam ac tempor ut eleifend auctor egestas laoreet. Convallis est tempus at quisque elementum et integer morbi orci. Elit ornare magna purus at ullamcorper metus. Massa libero aenean iaculis ultrices enim elit quisque malesuada praesent. Blandit morbi urna venenatis urna quis fringilla cras pellentesque. Sed interdum massa aliquam duis gravida consequat risus pharetra sem. Aliquam feugiat justo sit vulputate. Donec blandit convallis donec sit volutpat duis morbi. Ultrices tellus in et risus viverra eu et massa sagittis. Lorem quam nulla mi rhoncus.<\/p>","description_hn_replace":false,"show_more":false,"text_max_lines":3,"text_more":"Voir plus","text_less":"Voir moins","show_more_alignment":"center"}}},"block_order":["subheading_JWwFUp","heading_LzyUxg","text_mqaabX"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"